# Overview

This document defines the production-level database schema for the Schooly WebApp backend. The design reflects the current project implementation as defined in JPA entities and Flyway migrations.

The schema supports:

* Normalized relational architecture
* Scalable multi-school model
* Role-based access control
* Student lifecycle management
* Attendance tracking
* Financial operations for invoices and payments
* Parent and staff relationships
* Dashboard and analytics support

---

# Core Modules Covered

* Authentication & Authorization
* School Management
* Student Management
* Staff Management
* Parent Management
* Class & Section Management
* Attendance Management
* Fee & Invoice Management
* Payment Tracking
* Dashboard Analytics Support

