# Database Architecture

```text
schools
 ├── users
 │    ├── user_school_roles
 │    ├── auth_sessions
 │    └── student_parents
 ├── class
 │    └── student
 │         ├── student_attendance
 │         ├── fee_invoice
 │         │    └── payment
 │         └── student_parents
 ├── staff
 └── fee_invoice
```

