# 6. student_parents Table

Stores student-parent associations.

| Column         | Type        | Constraints                                 |
| -------------- | ----------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| student_id     | BIGINT      | NOT NULL, FOREIGN KEY → `student(id)`        |
| parent_user_id | BIGINT      | NOT NULL, FOREIGN KEY → `users(id)`          |
| relation       | VARCHAR(100)| NULL                                         |
| is_primary     | BOOLEAN     | NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE                       |

### Keys

* Primary key: composite `(student_id, parent_user_id)`

### Indexes

* `idx_student_parents_parent_user_id` on `parent_user_id`

